== Warnings ==
If either the begin or end templates are not properly transcluded, disaster may strike, causing the infobox to either swallow the article (missing the end template), or terminate unexpectedly (missing the begin template).

As with all collapsed content, if there are references to citations (<code><nowiki><ref>...</ref></nowiki></code>) inside collapsible sections, readers cannot jump to the location of the reference using the backlinks (^ or ''n''{{sup|a b c ...}}) at the citation.  Backlinks will only work when the collapsible section(s) is/are expanded.  The same is true for citations within a collapsed {{tl|collapsible list}} or {{tl|hidden}} template or any collapsed content.

